To build the application
ant
To deploy the application
edit the tomcat home in
conf/transport.conf
give mysql connection information in
src/org/transport/db/db.properties
ant deploy

Note:
1) you need  mysql-connector-java-3.0.16-ga-bin.jar(whichever version you have) and  servlet.jar
in the lib folder

2) When the transport module is integrated with the main sahana module then
   above settings may change

